### ==================== SMS 短信测试 ====================

### 发送短信（改成你验证过的手机号）
POST http://localhost:8888/api/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "+8615888441354",
  "message": "Hello from TeaTime! "
}

###

### 发送 MMS（带图片）
POST http://localhost:8888/api/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "+8615888441354",
  "message": "Check out our spa!",
  "mediaUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?w=400"
}

###

### 发送预约提醒
POST http://localhost:8888/api/sms/booking-reminder?to=+8615888441354&customerName=John&serviceName=Massage&appointmentTime=Tomorrow 2PM&staffName=Sarah

###

### 查询消息状态（替换成实际的 SID）
GET http://localhost:8888/api/sms/SMxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

###

### ==================== Voice 语音测试 ====================

### 发起外呼（简单朗读）
POST http://localhost:8888/api/voice/call
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "+14436163656",
  "record": true
}

###

### 发起外呼（IVR 菜单）
POST http://localhost:8888/api/voice/call
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "+14436163656",
  "record": false
}

###

### 发起预约确认电话
POST http://localhost:8888/api/voice/booking-call?to=++14436163656&customerName=John&serviceName=Deep Tissue Massage&appointmentTime=Tomorrow at 2 PM

###

### 查询通话状态（替换成实际的 SID）
GET http://localhost:8888/api/voice/CAxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

###

### 结束通话
POST http://localhost:8888/api/voice/CAxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx/end

###

### 获取通话录音
GET http://localhost:8888/api/voice/CAxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx/recordings